T* (attention back to warm ups. The twenty minutes we had for warm ups seemed to last no longer than) Tj
T* (two minutes. The announcer began to state our starting line up, but it was no use. The roar of) Tj
T* (the crowd overpowered the speaker system. It seemed as @CAPS7 everyone from our town of five) Tj
