T* (great way of communication, @CAPS1's are definately benefitting us. One reason why computers) Tj
T* (help us is by teaching hand-eye coordination. In a magazine I read, one expect, \(@PERSON1\) said) Tj
T* (that leading to type without looking is a great way of improving reflexes. The speed that you) Tj
T* (type is improved with practice. Another way it improves hand-eye coordination is by learning to) Tj
T* (click and react to different things effectively. I often on being ammused by playing games on) Tj
T* (the computer. These games usually are hard, but with my improving hand-eye coordination, I am) Tj
T* (learning how to play these games well. My father always tells me to learn my way through a) Tj
T* (computer because they are our future, soon, mostly everything will be done by them with the) Tj
T* (improving technokolgy, it is impossible for it not to be benificial to our society. Our home) Tj
T* (computers have been great at teaching me thing like hand-eye coordination. Another reason why) Tj
T* (computers are great is by making that tough history paper, just a click away. My garndfather) Tj
T* (always tells me how easy I have it. Instead of going to the @CAPS2 and having to pick out a) Tj
T* (book, I just go to google and have an entire search engine infront of me. When we go into) Tj
T* (highschool we will need a computer to suceed. To keep our essays organized, our research) Tj
T* (effective, and the clear to read typing right infront of us. My brother tells me that having a) Tj
T* (computer is the best investment has ever made. Last year, we had a science assignment to figure) Tj
