T* (destination of researchers, is to offer information that must be sought: for those who cannot) Tj
T* (find the information in their homes without fear, for those who cannot ask their questions) Tj
T* (without retribution, the library stands as a pillar of safety. Books are incapable of judgment.) Tj
T* (To censor the books held in a library is to chip away at human progress. A freedom of thought) Tj
