T* (not all books worthy of the same? To value one opinion or perspective less than another is to) Tj
T* (debase the entire culture from which libraries have arisen. Libraries are a communal) Tj
T* (institution, open to all views and writings. The point of bringing books together under one roof) Tj
T* (is to equate them, and give them all equal standing as literature or scholarly works. From) Tj
